description: The people of Portland just go loco for all the tasty comfort food that comes out of the famous Lobos Truck. This talented team is grilling up a mouthwatering selection of premium burgers, like The Chinook (⅓ lb. American-Kobe beef burger with garlic aioli, cheddar, lettuce, and tomato on a fresh-baked Brioche bun), and other classically satisfying cuisine, like Mac ‘N’ Cheese with bacon and hot wings. Watch out for this truck on the streets, so that you can order up their wonderful Wachos; crispy crunchy waffle fries, topped with a delicious twist on nacho fixins’, like their signature diablo/angel buffalo sauce, crumbled bleu cheese, savory bacon, scallions, and ranch. And for dessert, don’t forget to dig into their Salted Caramel Bacon Brownie...mmm...For all this and much, much more, come check out The Lobos Truck for a mobile meal you’re sure to love.
name: The Lobos Truck
